          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "This property applies to the entire text string. The default value of this property is the body style of the system font. "
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "aside",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "You can get information about the fonts available on the system using the methods of the "
